# Alfred Workflow Configuration Standards

## info.plist Structure
The [info.plist](mdc:info.plist) file is the core configuration for Alfred workflows.

### Essential Properties
```xml
<key>bundleid</key>
<string>com.username.workflowname</string>

<key>name</key>
<string>Workflow Display Name</string>

<key>description</key>
<string>Brief description of workflow functionality</string>

<key>version</key>
<string>1.0.0</string>

<key>createdby</key>
<string>Author Name</string>
```

### Workflow Variables
```xml
<key>variables</key>
<dict>
    <key>alfred_workflow_directory</key>
    <string>/path/to/workflow</string>
    <key>custom_variable</key>
    <string>custom_value</string>
</dict>
```

## Object Configuration Patterns

### Keyword Input
```xml
<dict>
    <key>config</key>
    <dict>
        <key>argumenttype</key>
        <integer>2</integer>  <!-- 0=required, 1=optional, 2=no argument -->
        <key>keyword</key>
        <string>keyword_trigger</string>
        <key>subtext</key>
        <string>Description shown below keyword</string>
        <key>text</key>
        <string>Main title text</string>
        <key>withspace</key>
        <false/>  <!-- Whether space is required after keyword -->
    </dict>
    <key>type</key>
    <string>alfred.workflow.input.keyword</string>
    <key>uid</key>
    <string>UNIQUE-UUID-HERE</string>
</dict>
```

### Script Action
```xml
<dict>
    <key>config</key>
    <dict>
        <key>concurrently</key>
        <false/>  <!-- Run concurrently with other actions -->
        <key>escaping</key>
        <integer>102</integer>  <!-- Escaping type -->
        <key>script</key>
        <string>cd "${alfred_workflow_directory}" && ./script.sh</string>
        <key>scriptargtype</key>
        <integer>1</integer>  <!-- Argument type -->
        <key>type</key>
        <integer>0</integer>  <!-- Script type: 0=bash -->
    </dict>
    <key>type</key>
    <string>alfred.workflow.action.script</string>
    <key>uid</key>
    <string>UNIQUE-UUID-HERE</string>
</dict>
```

### Copy to Clipboard Output
```xml
<dict>
    <key>config</key>
    <dict>
        <key>autopaste</key>
        <false/>  <!-- Automatically paste after copying -->
        <key>clipboardtext</key>
        <string>{query}</string>  <!-- Text to copy -->
        <key>transient</key>
        <false/>  <!-- Whether to keep in clipboard history -->
    </dict>
    <key>type</key>
    <string>alfred.workflow.output.clipboard</string>
    <key>uid</key>
    <string>UNIQUE-UUID-HERE</string>
</dict>
```

## Connection Configuration
```xml
<key>connections</key>
<dict>
    <key>SOURCE-UUID</key>
    <array>
        <dict>
            <key>destinationuid</key>
            <string>DESTINATION-UUID</string>
            <key>modifiers</key>
